<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Kan bu in kan i ton than tiangin, Nan sinah Pathian um ko seh, Amah
 nih him in keng ko seh, Amah chimhhrinnak in lam sial seh.

[C1]
   Kan i ton-than hlan tiang, Jesuh sin kan i ton tiang, Kan i ton than
   hlan tiang, Nanmah sinah Pathian um ko seh.

[V2]
 Kan bu in kan i ton than tiangin, Kan sinah Pathian um ko seh, A thla
 in in huppheng ko seh. Nifate in rawl in pe ko seh.

[C2]
   Kan i ton-than hlan tiang, Jesuh sin kan i ton tiang, Kan i ton than
   hlan tiang, Nanmah sinah Pathian um ko seh.

[V3]
 Kan bu in kan i ton than tiangin, Nan sinah Pathian um ko seh,
 Sifahnak kha na hmuh tikah, Nangmah kha a kut in pom ko seh.

[C3]
   Kan i ton-than hlan tiang, Jesuh sin kan i ton tiang, Kan i ton than
   hlan tiang, Nanmah sinah Pathian um ko seh.

[V4]
 Kan bu in kan i ton than tiangin, Kan sinah Pathian um ko seh, Dawt
 ngiatnak puan kha lek ko seh, Thihnak tilet kha daihter ko seh.

[C4]
   Kan i ton-than hlan tiang, Jesuh sin kan i ton tiang, Kan i ton than
   hlan tiang, Nanmah sinah Pathian um ko seh.</lyrics>
